data.description: Welcome to this fantastic 5 bedroom 4 bathroom 1.5 story home! Your gourmet open kitchen is truly extraordinary! It includes a huge center island, large dark wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel built-in appliances with a gas cooktop, and a beautiful tile backsplash. You will find your family room is open to the kitchen and a spacious breakfast area. The entertainment space continues out to an inviting covered patio in the backyard. The master suite includes a walk-in closet, ensuite bathroom with a separate dual vanity and garden tub. Upstairs has the 5th bedroom and a great bonus room that can be used as a game room, exercise room, playroom, you name it! 11926 Tower Creek is within walking distance from the neighborhood pool and park with a brand new playscape being built! Don't miss out on this spacious home perfect for entertaining guests!
